@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Pembayaran Tagihan & Verifikasi

actor Tenant
boundary "TenantBillingScreen" as UI_T
control "PembayaranController" as API
database "Pembayarans Table" as DB
actor Owner
boundary "OwnerTransactionList" as UI_O

== Proses Pembayaran (Tenant) ==
Tenant -> UI_T : Input Bukti & Pilih Metode
UI_T -> API : POST /api/pembayaran/upload-bukti/{id}
activate API
API -> DB : Update status='menunggu_konfirmasi', bukti_bayar, metode
activate DB
DB --> API : Success
deactivate DB
API --> UI_T : JSON {message: 'Berhasil lapor'}
deactivate API

== Proses Verifikasi (Owner) ==
Owner -> UI_O : Refresh Data Transaksi
UI_O -> API : GET /api/pembayaran
API -> DB : Fetch All Transactions
DB --> API : List Transactions
API --> UI_O : List UI
Owner -> UI_O : Klik Konfirmasi (ID)
UI_O -> API : POST /api/pembayaran/konfirmasi/{id}
activate API
API -> DB : Update status='lunas'
activate DB
DB --> API : Success
deactivate DB
API --> UI_O : JSON {message: 'Pembayaran Lunas'}
deactivate API

@enduml
